      <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p style='margin-bottom: 12px;'&gt;Before starting activation, please complete these steps:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style='margin: 10px 0;'&gt;&lt;b style='color: #3b82f6;'&gt;📶 Step 1:&lt;/b&gt; Connect your device to &lt;b&gt;WiFi&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

