&lt;p style='margin: 10px 0;'&gt;&lt;b style='color: #3b82f6;'&gt;✓ Step 3:&lt;/b&gt; Ensure device shows activation lock screen&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style='margin-top: 16px; color: #6b7280;'&gt;Click 'Continue' when ready to begin activation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
